I"r<p>In this first episode, I interview uMkhonto we Sizwe military veteran <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ian.beddowes.77">Ian Beddowes</a></p>

<p>We explore the concept of imperialism as well as its importance. Intro background music is “Saramugomo” by Mbira Dzenharira.
Outro music is “Ballard of Accounting” by Ewan MacColl and Peggy Seeger. Episode Artwork is The Rhodes Colossus from Wikimedia Commons.</p>

